Description: 2016 Custom Build Blackout Contemporary ST Strat Style Axe. Black-Silver Paisley Modified Thin The Herd I pulled out all the garbage in this new axe and loaded it with a sweet black, paisley pickguard and back plate. Custom engraved paisley neck plate added. Roller string trees, locking tuners, strap locks, all Fender Strat Standard Ceramic pickups and electronics. Also added Chicken Head knobs. Really brought it to life. The black outline on the headstock and the black filled in area on the cutout of the headstock were simply colored in with a black Sharpie....so, it's easily removable with nail polish remover if you would lie. It truly ended up being a great guitar. I bought 4 guitars from them to modify and have some fun doing so. Comes with a new hardshell case! Original ad when I purchased it: 2016 Custom Build Blackout Contemporary ST Blacked out ST. Modeled after the 80's Contemporary strats. Loaded, check it out... Mahogany body. Black pickguard loaded with unbranded Korean single coils. Overwound pickups for sweet blues tones! Upgraded Fender-style half moon switch and full sized pots. This gets a wide range of tones. Bridge tone setup. Lower tone controls bridge, middle tone location controls middle/neck pickups. Rosewood on Maple neck! Polished frets. Smoooth. Our Custom Build logo lets folks know this is no generic strat! Fresh set of D'Addario 10 46's. 14" radius, C profile. Black sealed tuners. Bone nut. Includes our custom Screamin' Eagle headstock design. Blackout hardware including tremolo, output jack, tuners and pickguard. Play a few times by locals making demo clips for our guitars - minor signs of use - protective plastic taken off guard, small indention at the base of the back of the neck. Other than that this is one mean looking guitar. Ships to lower 48 US states.Fully insured.
Title: 2016 Custom Build Blackout Contemporary ST Strat Style Axe. Black-Silver Paisley
